[Civil No. 773.] JAMES A. CARROW, Administrator of the Estate of Fred E. Carrow, Deceased, v. THE MUTUAL LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY OF NEW YORK, Appellee. APPEAL from the District Court of the Fourth Judicial District in and for the County of Mohave. Richard E. Sloan, Judge. W. H. Stilwell, Attorney for Appellee. February 12, 1902.

No appearance for Appellant.

Affirmed on short transcript under par. 1583, Rev. Stats. Ariz. 1901.
